2182338, "replies": 27, "id": 803133}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 2579, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785", "stars": 651, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"username": "manami", "website": "https://fffdann.com", "github": "", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9166/4abd/453453_mini.png?m=1632145903", "bio": "我们的征途是星辰大海！", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/manami", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1573871499, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9166/4abd/453453_mini.png?m=1632145903", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9166/4abd/453453_mini.png?m=1632145903", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 453453}, "last_reply_by": "manami", "last_touched": 1632194542, "title": "想要变得酷酷的，有没有什么快捷的办法？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/803103", "created": 1632148197, "content": "标题可能说得不太清楚，就是想在衣着搭配上或者发型上改进一下，想要改掉刻板的直男形象\r\n\r\n最近接触异性的机会较多，她们反馈的结果就是觉得我颜值尚可，就是穿着过于普通呆板。说是有很大改进空间，不知道是不是骗我 /笑哭\r\n\r\n日常我最常见的搭配是牛仔裤+纯色 T 恤，她们建议我可以专门做个发型（碎盖头），再买个这几年流行的遮阳帽（渔夫帽）。\r\n\r\n这种搭配给我的第一感觉是太 fashion 了（可能是自己太土了 QAQ ），直男程序员（不过应该很快就不做程序员了）一下子改成这个设定坐地铁会不会 hold 不住 2333 \r\n\r\n但是自己确实想要做出一些改变，试试也未尝不可\r\n\r\nV 友们有没有尝试过类似的自我改造，有没有好的建议，提前感谢\r\n\r\n我在网上找了样张，如下\r\n\r\n![https://files.catbox.moe/xy72or.jpg]( https://files.catbox.moe/xy72or.jpg)\r\n![https://files.catbox.moe/f9kdqb.jpg]( https://files.catbox.moe/f9kdqb.jpg)", "content_rendered": "<p>标题可能说得不太清楚，就是想在衣着搭配上或者发型上改进一下，想要改掉刻板的直男形象</p>\n<p>最近接触异性的机会较多，她们反馈的结果就是觉得我颜值尚可，就是穿着过于普通呆板。说是有很大改进空间，不知道是不是骗我 /笑哭</p>\n<p>日常我最常见的搭配是牛仔裤+纯色 T 恤，她们建议我可以专门做个发型（碎盖头），再买个这几年流行的遮阳帽（渔夫帽）。</p>\n<p>这种搭配给我的第一感觉是太 fashion 了（可能是自己太土了 QAQ ），直男程序员（不过应该很快就不做程序员了）一下子改成这个设定坐地铁会不会 hold 不住 2333 </p>\n<p>但是自己确实想要做出一些改变，试试也未尝不可</p>\n<p>V 友们有没有尝试过类似的自我改造，有没有好的建议，提前感谢</p>\n<p>我在网上找了样张，如下</p>\n<p><img alt=\"https://files.catbox.moe/xy72or.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/xy72or.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"https://files.catbox.moe/f9kdqb.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/f9kdqb.jpg\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1632148396, "replies": 26, "id": 803103}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/069d/3bb0/580_large.png?m=1611468295", "name": "ios", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/069d/3bb0/580_normal.png?m=1611468295", "title": "iOS", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/ios", "topics": 2743, "footer": "", "header": "运行于 Apple 移动设备上的操作系统。", "title_alternative": "iOS", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/069d/3bb0/580_mini.png?m=1611468295", "stars": 669, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 580, "parent_node_name": "apple"}, "member": {"username": "shutongxinq", "website": "", "github": "", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6d937a9ffee1690b867c0b6bb66ce1c8?s=24&d=retro", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/shutongxinq", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1422456671, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6d937a9ffee1690b867c0b6bb66ce1c8?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6d937a9ffee1690b867c0b6bb66ce1c8?s=24&d=retro", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 94411}, "last_reply_by": "MyKey", "last_touched": 1632207581, "title": "iOS15 延期的功能真不少", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/803125", "created": 1632160886, "content": "iOS15 这次延期的功能真不少\r\n\r\n1. **SharePlay** (fall): 主打功能就这么赤裸裸延期了\r\n2. **ID cards** (this year): 少带驾照的功能又成了 ppt\r\n3. **CarPlay 3D 导航** (later date): 期待的功能成了镜花水月\r\n4. **Universal Control** (later this year): 最期待的功能还在测试\r\n5. **Find My AirPods** (later update): 如果最近丢 AirPods，找回没有预想中的容易\r\n6. **Digital Car Keys** (later in 2021): 这个功能延期可能暂时还好，毕竟老车不支持。\r\n7. **隐私报告** (2021 or 2022): 小米的照明弹看来不好抄，可能今年都不会准备就绪\r\n8. **自定义 iCloud 域名** (later): 反正就是没有 ready\r\n\r\n所以说，这次 iOS15.0 更新是否可以理解为 66%的功能还没有 ready ？\r\n\r\n看来在家工作还真是摸鱼。", "content_rendered": "<p>iOS15 这次延期的功能真不少</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>SharePlay</strong> (fall): 主打功能就这么赤裸裸延期了</li>\n<li><strong>ID cards</strong> (this year): 少带驾照的功能又成了 ppt</li>\n<li><strong>CarPlay 3D 导航</strong> (later date): 期待的功能成了镜花水月</li>\n<li><strong>Universal Control</strong> (later this year): 最期待的功能还在测试</li>\n<li><strong>Find My AirPods</strong> (later update): 如果最近丢 AirPods，找回没有预想中的容易</li>\n<li><strong>Digital Car Keys</strong> (later in 2021): 这个功能延期可能暂时还好，毕竟老车不支持。</li>\n<li><strong>隐私报告</strong> (2021 or 2022): 小米的照明弹看来不好抄，可能今年都不会准备就绪</li>\n<li><strong>自定义 iCloud 域名</strong> (later): 反正就是没有 ready</li>\n</ol>\n<p>所以说，这次 iOS15.0 更新是否可以理解为 66%的功能还没有 ready ？</p>\n<p>看来在家工作还真是摸鱼。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1632160898, "replies": 25, "id": 803125}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/069d/3bb0/580_large.png?m=1611468295", "name": "ios", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/069d/3bb0/580_normal.png?m=1611468295", "title": "iOS", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/ios", "topics": 2743, "footer": "", "header": "运行于 Apple 移动设备上的操作系统。", "title_alternative": "iOS", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/069d/3bb0/580_mini.png?m=1611468295", "stars": 669, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 580, "parent_node_name": "apple"}, "member": {"username": "q1angch0u", "website": "", "github": "", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6af8/2dad/459675_mini.png?m=1616736801", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/q1angch0u", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1576555510, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6af8/2dad/459675_mini.png?m=1616736801", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6af8/2dad/459675_mini.png?m=1616736801", "location"